items.description:
Boris Brejcha - Universe Of Love
Fckng Serious 2023
__
Boris Brejcha, also known as "The Joker," is back with his next single! On September 24th, his new single, "Dimension," will be released, giving us another glimpse into his upcoming album set to be released next year.
Fans can particularly look forward to this single because "Dimension" doesn't come alone. Alongside this main track, the German producer is also releasing another song called "Universe Of Love."
Both tracks are currently solid additions to Boris Brejcha's sets during his sold-out concerts around the world. This year has been phenomenal for the masked artist. In addition to major festivals in Europe and the USA, Boris has played numerous of his own In Concert Shows, setting new standards and immersing audiences in a unique concert world.
To keep his fans from waiting any longer, he is now releasing the next single from his album scheduled for 2024, following "Level One," "Space X," and "Vienna."
Both tracks carry Boris Brejcha's unmistakable touch, which he often describes as High-Tech Minimal. The driving basslines that penetrate the body are a distinctive feature of this release. "Dimension" aims to take the listener thematically into another dimension, echoing the overall theme of the album. On the other hand, "Universe Of Love" exudes a more playful and affectionate melody, creating a contrasting vibe.
Get ready for the next rocket ride to another world. Boris Brejcha invites us into a different dimension with his next release! Both tracks will be released on Boris Brejcha's own label, Fckng Serious, and will be available for download and streaming on all platforms starting November 24, 2023. We can hardly wait!
